Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教会里\N{\rEng}In the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们常常不知道如何与周围\N{\rEng}we often don’t know how to relate to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在挣扎的朋友或... 家人建立起联系\N{\rEng}friends or... or family members who are struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着很多人 甚至我们教会中的人\N{\rEng}That means a lot of people, even in our church,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是孤独的\N{\rEng}feel really alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此让我们示以他们爱\N{\rEng}So let's show them our love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在上帝的关怀下为这些孩子送行\N{\rEng}and send these boys off in the embrace of God's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔·李 迈克尔·蓝道夫 本杰明·埃利斯\N{\rEng}Joe Lee, Michael Randolph and Benjamin Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请上来\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是你们\N{\rEng}Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们 请跟我一起站到台上来\N{\rEng}Gentlemen, please join me up here on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱格堡 - 陆军空降兵与特种部队驻地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们祈祷 亲爱的主\N{\rEng}We pray, dear Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你保佑这些仗剑执盾之人...\N{\rEng}for those that wield the swords so that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并让正义得到胜利\N{\rEng}that righteousness may triumph
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让邪恶必然败亡\N{\rEng}and wrongdoings may be vanquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对於这些保卫我们的人\N{\rEng}For these men are our protectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请上帝你 能宽慰他们的家人\N{\rEng}Lord, please comfort their families
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他们被派往前线驻派时\N{\rEng}while these men are deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赐予所有这些孩子特别的恩典\N{\rEng}Bestow special grace upon all these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿上帝祝福你们 保佑你们\N{\rEng}May God bless you and protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿上帝保佑美国 阿门\N{\rEng}And may God bless America. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\rEng}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我并不想吵醒你的\N{\rEng}Sorry. I didn’t want to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我早已经醒了\N{\rEng}That's all right. I was already awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练进行得怎样了 \N{\rEng}How's training going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是否还有时间来滚个床单 \N{\rEng}Do we have time for night sex or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他已经醒了\N{\rEng}I think he's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他今天总要去学校吧 \N{\rEng}Doesn’t he have school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 今天是周六\N{\rEng}No, it's Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在周六都不上课的吗 \N{\rEng}Aren’t they in school on Saturdays?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1953年起就不上了\N{\rEng}Not since 1953.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢1953年 那年头很棒\N{\rEng}I liked 1953 a lot. It's a great year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟爸爸打个招呼吗 \N{\rEng}Want to say hi to Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你手里拿的是什么 \N{\rEng}Hey, Dad. What you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\rEng}Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你在飞机上\N{\rEng}That's you in the airplane. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是云彩\N{\rEng}And those are the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一整周都在忙着画这个给你\N{\rEng}He's been working on that all week for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画的真棒\N{\rEng}That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来帮帮我 好的 来吧\N{\rEng}Give us a hand. Okay. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克  你在哪呢  我就在你身后 爸爸\N{\rEng}Jack? Jack? I’m right behind you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克  你在哪呢  爸爸 我就在这\N{\rEng}Jack? Jack? Dad, I’m right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你能行的\N{\rEng}Come on. You got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\rEng}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就陪在这里 好吗 \N{\rEng}I’m gonna be right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要什么 我就在你身旁\N{\rEng}If you need anything, I’m gonna be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 准备好没 \N{\rEng}All right. You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 嗯 你行的\N{\rEng}No. Yeah, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请不要离开我\N{\rEng}No. Please don’t leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有离开你 我就在这呢\N{\rEng}I’m not leaving you. I’m right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克 看着我\N{\rEng}Jack, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1\N{\rEng}Three... two... one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 放松 孩子 然后游向我这\N{\rEng}Now, let go, son. Swim to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你能行的\N{\rEng}No. You’ve got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 放松 看着我\N{\rEng}That's it. Let go. Eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脚打水\N{\rEng}Use your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 你会游泳了 杰克\N{\rEng}That's it! You’re swimming, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会游泳了 加油\N{\rEng}You’re swimming. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做到了 杰克 你会游泳了 加油\N{\rEng}You’re doing it, Jack. You’re swimming. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你游得很好 儿子\N{\rEng}You did good, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我做到了\N{\rEng}Mom! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你做到了 我做到了\N{\rEng}Yeah, you did. I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我想我会游泳了 你看\N{\rEng}Dad, I think I can swim now. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来\N{\rEng}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看看\N{\rEng}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7个月长高一英寸\N{\rEng}An inch in seven months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7个月长高一英寸 你觉得呢 \N{\rEng}An inch in seven months. How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很厉害吗  当然 很不得了了\N{\rEng}Is that enough? That's a lot. That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是负责账单管理的希拉\N{\rEng}Hi, this is Sheila from Bills Recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想问下你们账单逾期的情况...\N{\rEng}I just wanna check in with y’all on your past due paym...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信息已删除\N{\rEng}Message deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 听着 夥计 很抱歉打扰了你的周末\N{\rEng}Hey, James. Listen, man, I’m sorry to ruin your weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但指挥官在对全队进行检测\N{\rEng}but the CO is testing the whole team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你最好过来下\N{\rEng}Uh, you better get down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆军一级军士 詹姆斯·哈珀\N{\rEng}Army Sergeant First Class James Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍息 军士\N{\rEng}At ease, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是我们的新指挥官 罗伯茨中校\N{\rEng}This is our new CO, Lieutenant Colonel Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膝关节二度撕裂\N{\rEng}Knee was shredded. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康复进展得很好 谢谢 长官\N{\rEng}Great job with the rehab. Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肺部不再适合执行高空或水下任务\N{\rEng}Your lung precludes high altitude or underwater operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个肺陪我在5年中进行了4次战斗轮值 长官\N{\rEng}I’ve done four combat rotations in five years with that lung, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放轻点 哈珀军士\N{\rEng}You can relax, Sergeant Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血检还显示 你体内药物残留有\N{\rEng}Blood work came back filthy with Stanozolol,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康力龙 诺龙 苯丙酸诺龙 生长激素\N{\rEng}Nandrolone, phenylpropionate and HGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为特种部队医务官\N{\rEng}You’re an SOF medical sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该很清楚这些药\N{\rEng}Should have known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在队里 长官 我是为了想留在队里\N{\rEng}I wanted to stay on the team, sir. I wanted to stay on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么前指挥官会纵容你这样做\N{\rEng}I have no idea what your previous COs encouraged,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我的治下我绝不允许\N{\rEng}but I won’t accept that in my unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大队决定撤销你的特种部队军职\N{\rEng}Big Army recommended a revocation of your Special Forces tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样的做法很不对 换我是不会这样做的\N{\rEng}And although I disagree with your choices, I’m not going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将会以荣誉退伍身份离开军队\N{\rEng}You’re leaving the army with an honorable discharge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你将失去你的福利 其中包括你的退休金和医疗保险\N{\rEng}but you’re losing your benefits, which include your pension and health care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散\N{\rEng}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯\N{\rEng}James.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着说什么 听着 他们无非想清理门户\N{\rEng}- You don’t have to say anything. - Look. They’re cleaning house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是被抓了个正着 我认了 我能理解\N{\rEng}- You made it easy for them. - I’ll own up. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的声誉\N{\rEng}With your rep,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你退伍后肯定会有大把私人军事承包商来抢着找你\N{\rEng}every private's gonna be hitting on you the second you walk off post.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为膝盖吃了那些药 然后被血检发现了 这就是原因\N{\rEng}I took shit for my knee. They found it in my blood. That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样了  就再也没其他办法了 \N{\rEng}So that's it? And there's nothing you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 他们就是临时搞个狗屁规则...\N{\rEng}So, they just basically made up a new bullshit rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有搞什么... 让测试...\N{\rEng}- They didn’t make up a... - Test...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是什么临时狗屁规则\N{\rEng}No, they didn’t make up any bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不说大队多年都没检测过任何人\N{\rEng}You said they haven’t tested anybody in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样 就算他要搞 这也合情合理\N{\rEng}They haven’t tested anyone in years. But it's legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次检测纯粹就是新指挥官硬搞的...\N{\rEng}It's the new CO that has a fucking hard-on for just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 他无非想清理门户\N{\rEng}I don’t know, he just wants to clear house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上尉告诉我的 说他们想清理门户\N{\rEng}That's what the captain told me. They wanna clear house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 \N{\rEng}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催收公司寄来的\N{\rEng}It’s, um, debt collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经和他们谈过了\N{\rEng}But I already talked to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说 他们能为我们制定一个计划\N{\rEng}And, uh, they said they could help us with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的利率是多少 \N{\rEng}What's the interest rate on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18%\N{\rEng}It's 18%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听着... 还有个工作可以干 而且能拿大把的钱\N{\rEng}Yeah. There is... There's real work out there with real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人承包商  嗯\N{\rEng}Private contracting? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 为何不呢 \N{\rEng}Mm-mmm. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你说过你不会去干这个的\N{\rEng}No. You said you weren’t gonna do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道我说过什么\N{\rEng}I know what I said. I know what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rEng}Mm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布鲁斯·迈克斯\N{\rEng}This is Bruce Michaels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自贴身保镖公司\N{\rEng}with Executive Protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你从军队里荣誉退伍\N{\rEng}Congrats on your years of decorated service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很乐意为你提供工作\N{\rEng}We’d love to discuss opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈珀先生 我是大卫\N{\rEng}Mr. Harper, my name is David.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从水电部打给你的\N{\rEng}I’m calling from the Department of Water and Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信息已删除\N{\rEng}Message deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 \N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在坏天气来之前...\N{\rEng}Just putting up some shingles before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把屋顶给修理好\N{\rEng}before we get weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们儿子呢 \N{\rEng}Where's our son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他睡着了 今天给他累趴下了\N{\rEng}Oh, he's asleep. He's down for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做的挺多 但...\N{\rEng}Took him a bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校... 在学校过得怎样 \N{\rEng}How was, uh... How was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能先下来吗  嗯 就稍微等我一会\N{\rEng}- Can you come down? - Yeah, I’ll come down in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就快修完了\N{\rEng}I just have a couple more to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我有事要告诉你\N{\rEng}Honey, I got something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就弄完 不 现在就下来\N{\rEng}- I’ll be down in a minute. - No. Like, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了很快就弄完 布瑞安\N{\rEng}I’ll be down in a minute, Brianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅森去世了\N{\rEng}Mason's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 \N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅森 他去世了\N{\rEng}Mason. He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 我才和苏珊谈完\N{\rEng}I... I just talked to Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么死的 \N{\rEng}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 \N{\rEng}How do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼在什么时候  明天\N{\rEng}- When's the funeral? - It's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们该打电话给你妈妈 让她来照看下杰克\N{\rEng}Maybe we should call your mom and see if she can take Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会去的\N{\rEng}I’m not gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然得去 布瑞安\N{\rEng}Of course we’re gonna go, Brianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不会去 因为我怕去了那联想到你\N{\rEng}No, I’m not gonna go. ’Cause I can’t go to another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在干嘛 \N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  你大半夜的跑屋顶上去到底是干什么 \N{\rEng}-What? -What are you doing on the roof in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在修理屋顶\N{\rEng}I’m fixing the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\rEng}I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\rEng}I’m just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是梅森对苏珊所说的话\N{\rEng}That's exactly what Mason said to Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在真的很害怕\N{\rEng}I’m really fucking scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我父亲不同\N{\rEng}I’m not my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会讨厌这个的\N{\rEng}He would’ve hated this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下葬仪式还是死亡 \N{\rEng}The ceremony or dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得又胖又丑\N{\rEng}Just being fat and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们是如何把他那大屁股塞进棺材的 \N{\rEng}How do you figure they shoved his giant butt into that grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他穿的是丁字裤\N{\rEng}He's wearing a thong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是怎么了 \N{\rEng}How’d he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指什么 \N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在睡梦中去世的\N{\rEng}He died in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人有拿到全额赔付吗 \N{\rEng}The family get full payout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了\N{\rEng}Full payout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\rEng}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆去我那吃顿晚餐吧  不了\N{\rEng}- Why don’t you come over for dinner? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没看过我的新家呢\N{\rEng}You haven’t seen the new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样说定了 你现在变得越来越无趣了\N{\rEng}You’re coming to dinner. You’re as moody as he was fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的 也去你的\N{\rEng}Fuck you. - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到你真好 很高兴你来了\N{\rEng}Good to see you. Glad you’re here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 你的家真漂亮\N{\rEng}Appreciate it. You have a beautiful home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夥计 玩的怎样了 \N{\rEng}Hey, bud. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要玩电子游戏吗 \N{\rEng}You wanna play a video game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了... 我当然要来玩 看看这个\N{\rEng}When do I... When do I not wanna play a video game? Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白袜队\N{\rEng}- Hey. - The White Sox.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 漂亮\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢白袜队 嗯 真没看出来\N{\rEng}I love the White Sox. - Yeah. Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  我是真喜欢白袜队 凯莉\N{\rEng}- What? I like the White Sox. - Hey, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯叔叔\N{\rEng}Hi, Uncle James.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 \N{\rEng}You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要带我参观 还是说要给我张地图 \N{\rEng}You gonna give me a tour, or should I just get a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是的\N{\rEng}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了\N{\rEng}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 看我的\N{\rEng}Yeah? Well, watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,265)}投的真好 就犹如{\u1}罗杰·克莱门斯{\u0} （*罗杰·克莱门斯：绰号"火箭人"  是活跃於1980年至2000年代的美职棒明星投手）\N{\rEng}Really good arm. - Roger Clemens over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你赐予我们这顿美餐\N{\rEng}Thank you for this meal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及感谢你把詹姆斯叔叔安全带了回来\N{\rEng}and thank you for bringing Uncle James back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\rEng}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门 阿门\N{\rEng}Amen. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁才是最好的士兵 你还是我爸爸 \N{\rEng}Who was a better soldier, you or my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你爸爸是我的长官 所以...\N{\rEng}Well, uh, your dad was my chief, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心你要说的话\N{\rEng}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的上级\N{\rEng}I was his superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们呢....\N{\rEng}Oh. But we were, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢  我们彼此互相照应\N{\rEng}How would you say? We looked after each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像兄弟那样\N{\rEng}Oh, kinda like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就像兄弟那样...\N{\rEng}Yeah, kinda like brothers. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的有救了我爸爸的命吗 \N{\rEng}Is it true you actually saved my dad's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 是的\N{\rEng}No. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有次 他把我从酒吧里拉出来\N{\rEng}Once. He pulled me out of a bar once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他喝醉了\N{\rEng}Yeah, he was a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲醉的爬都爬不起\N{\rEng}Your father was an absolute wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想这么早就告诉你\N{\rEng}I hate to break it to you this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 不 扫兴\N{\rEng}I... No. - Bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 米奇喜欢棒球 但他永远都没法玩\N{\rEng}Well, uh, Mikey loves baseball. He’ll never play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在抗争着呢 他...\N{\rEng}He's fighting it. He’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出他很坚强\N{\rEng}No quit in his DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法抗争赢的\N{\rEng}There's no beating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就算最好的情况 他的余生都需要特殊照顾\N{\rEng}Well, best case, he’ll need special care for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过得怎么样 \N{\rEng}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 嗯 很好\N{\rEng}Good. Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你呢 \N{\rEng}Yeah. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是说 也很好\N{\rEng}Yeah, good. I mean, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真很好 你就不会失联两个月 所以怎么了 \N{\rEng}You don’t fall off the grid for two months if you’re good. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对未来有什么期待 \N{\rEng}What do you look forward to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我的孩子长大\N{\rEng}Watching my kids grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着他们的笑脸\N{\rEng}Seeing ’em smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为他们做最好的安排 给与他们我不曾拥有的\N{\rEng}Making sure they’re set. Giving them the things I didn’t have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把事情捋捋清楚\N{\rEng}I gotta get my shit straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮忙嘛\N{\rEng}There's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 让我去干办公室的活  不 门都没有\N{\rEng}No. Kill any operational future? No, not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人承包商有联系我\N{\rEng}Privates contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 嗯\N{\rEng}Good. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 这很好 你应该去赚这钱\N{\rEng}Yeah. No, fuck yeah. You deserve a paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,账单压我身上 我只能... 别想了 去干吧\N{\rEng}Bank is on my ass, and I just... Hell yeah. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经也去干过几次活\N{\rEng}I pulled a couple of cowboy tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的 干完之后 银行里的存款有了 买房子的钱也有了\N{\rEng}You know, banked some decent cash, put a down payment on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿油油的钱 也就花个5 6天\N{\rEng}Cash is real. You know, five, six a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有奖金 这累积起来\N{\rEng}Bonuses, you know, it adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是大把的钱\N{\rEng}It's okay to cash in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  现在就纯他妈吃人的社会\N{\rEng}You know, it's pure fuckin’ Darwin out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以好好利用我们的所学去应对这环境\N{\rEng}And we are trained to be ruthlessly adaptable. Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正在哪不都是给别人干\N{\rEng}We’re all just mercenaries in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,265)}所以你现在在哪里干 {\u1}JSOC{\u0}还是联邦机构 {\fs14\c&HC38E15&}（*JSOC：美国联合特种作战司令部）\N{\rEng}So what do you got going now? Is it JSOC? Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之间\N{\rEng}Uh, in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬虽没私人承包商给的高 但国家认可它的合法性\N{\rEng}It doesn’t pay as good as private, but it's legit NatSec work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也出身於军队 人很好 非常可靠\N{\rEng}He's one of us. Good people. Rock-solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少钱 \N{\rEng}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35万\N{\rEng}Oh, 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能让我进去吗 \N{\rEng}Can you get me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是他妈和总统握过手的英雄\N{\rEng}Fucking hero? President shook your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的 他和很多人都握过手\N{\rEng}Fuck off. He shakes a lot of hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果他们就因为血检问题将我除名\N{\rEng}They pulled my clearances because of blood work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 只要你准备好 开口就行\N{\rEng}At this level, as long as you’re good to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯蒂并不关心你身体里打过什么\N{\rEng}Rusty doesn’t care what you put in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我个\N{\rEng}I’m in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想好了没有  我已经想好了\N{\rEng}- Is that what you want? - That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我破产了 迈克 我需要这活\N{\rEng}I’m broke, Mike. I need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你名字报过去\N{\rEng}I’ll send your name up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我会安排会面\N{\rEng}All right. I’ll set up a meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢了\N{\rEng}Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\rEng}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当只剩下我时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是哪里做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 夥计们  嘿 夥计\N{\rEng}- What's up, fellas? - Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是詹姆斯 我曾经的老队友 他在哪里 \N{\rEng}This is James, old running mate of mine. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪里 你何不也顺带过来搭把手帮帮我们 \N{\rEng}You know where he's at. Why don’t you give us a hand every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在18岁以前不停的辗转於男孩之家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 有没什么好吃的给我 \N{\rEng}Yo, Chief. Got anything tasty for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真他妈的甜\N{\rEng}Like fucking candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切诺基紫番茄\N{\rEng}Hmm, Cherokee Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到你\N{\rEng}It's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 长官\N{\rEng}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别长官来长官去的 叫我拉斯蒂 拉斯蒂·詹宁斯\N{\rEng}You can cut the "sir" crap. My name is Rusty, Rusty Jennings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 迈克\N{\rEng}Thanks, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意帮我拿下靴子吗 \N{\rEng}Hey, you mind grabbing my boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\rEng}Hey, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要来瓶啤酒吗 \N{\rEng}You want a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢\N{\rEng}I’m good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克是我共事过最好的人\N{\rEng}Mike's the best I ever worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说你是他共事过最好的人\N{\rEng}He says you’re the best he's ever worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 嗯 他... 他教会了我所知道的一切\N{\rEng}Yeah. Well, he, uh... He taught me everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的声誉 是我们在这场游戏里唯一能留下的\N{\rEng}Our reputation is the only commodity we got left in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看了我的故事 \N{\rEng}You reading my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 我的 迈克的 梅森的\N{\rEng}Yours, mine, Mike’s, Mason’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都他妈有着同样的故事 甚至你父亲也是\N{\rEng}It's all the same fucking story. Shit, even your father’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲和这好像并没有关系\N{\rEng}My father has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言\N{\rEng}Due respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言... 他当然有\N{\rEng}And due respect... sure he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把我们的思想 身体 精神交给了军队\N{\rEng}We gave them our minds, our bodies and our spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我们被他们用完即弃\N{\rEng}And they chewed us up and spit us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留给我们的只有恐惧 愤怒 人生的不确定\N{\rEng}Left us with fear, rage, uncertainty,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们感到失望 被抛弃 被背叛\N{\rEng}disillusionment, a sense of abandonment, betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我们变得自责 内疚\N{\rEng}And finally, self-loathing and guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些事的原因归咎到我们身上 搞得好像全我们的错一样\N{\rEng}As if somehow, everything that happened to us was our own goddamn fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全理解你现在的处境 孩子\N{\rEng}I know exactly where you are right now, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾和你一样\N{\rEng}I was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的 我们都曾这样\N{\rEng}Hell, we all were.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们才要抱团取暖\N{\rEng}That's why we started our own tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道在你面前的路有很多\N{\rEng}I know you got options in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.38,0:24:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是想拿高薪的话\N{\rEng}And if you’re looking for a big payday,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多顶级公司都能给你\N{\rEng}the top tiers can give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三叶丛林 宙斯盾 以及那头蠢猪 埃里克·普林斯\N{\rEng}Triple Canopy, Aegis and that soulless fuck-pig, Erik Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要你听听我的话\N{\rEng}But I need you to hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.72,0:24:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为都是真心的\N{\rEng}’cause I mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这些公司做事 只会玷污你身上的荣誉\N{\rEng}The stink from those gigs, it will rub off on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.48,0:24:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要说什么 \N{\rEng}So what is it that you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说你能为我提供不同的东西 \N{\rEng}You offer up something different or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说对了\N{\rEng}Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.24,0:25:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能给你真正的归属 光荣的工作\N{\rEng}I can give you a real home, honorable work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.83,0:25:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没利益往来 不为亿万富豪服务 也没任何狗屁事\N{\rEng}No corporate interest, no babysitting billionaires, no bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根据法典第50条 受总统直接授权行事\N{\rEng}We operate with direct presidential authority under Title 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.58,0:25:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格处理涉及国家安全相关事务\N{\rEng}Deal strictly with matters of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.96,0:25:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们隶属於秘密机构\N{\rEng}A deep black OGA offshoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.13,0:25:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第50条 我熟悉的很\N{\rEng}Title 50. I know those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经也根据这条行事\N{\rEng}We worked together downrange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.89,0:25:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以进出口咖啡为掩护\N{\rEng}We import and export coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.35,0:25:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夥计 你当兵时干的那些活都是粗活\N{\rEng}Man, what you did in uniform, sledgehammer shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们干的是精细活\N{\rEng}Our thing, scalpel work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.07,0:25:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做事低调 雷厉风行 只有必要时才动手\N{\rEng}High-speed, low drag, fangs only come out when they have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柏林有一个威胁到我们国家安全的情况\N{\rEng}There's a situation in Berlin that threatens our national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.08,0:25:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴於我们的存在属於机密\N{\rEng}The team led by Mike will be fully black
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.20,0:25:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克会领导一支秘密队伍前往\N{\rEng}since our presence is not approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多久 \N{\rEng}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两周 顶多三周\N{\rEng}Two weeks. Three, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你怎么说 你愿意加入我们吗 \N{\rEng}So what do you say? You down for the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.92,0:25:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然\N{\rEng}Yeah. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:25:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 迈克和道尔顿会帮你搞定入职手续\N{\rEng}Excellent. Mike and Dalton will walk you through the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间 布莱安和杰克显然...\N{\rEng}In the meantime, Brianne and Jack obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.64,0:26:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟这个事有什么关系 \N{\rEng}Uh, what do they have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.60,0:26:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 等你回来之后\N{\rEng}Well, when you get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我们大家能一起吃个饭什么的\N{\rEng}be nice if we all got together and broke some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.11,0:26:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 道尔顿会给你一张5万的支票\N{\rEng}But for now, Dalton's gonna cut you a check for 50K.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.52,0:26:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你跟我们干起活来也能安心点\N{\rEng}So you’re not sweating them while you’re working with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.99,0:26:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么白天关机了 \N{\rEng}Why was your phone off?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.22,0:26:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到份工作\N{\rEng}I got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.18,0:26:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到份工作 \N{\rEng}You got a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到份什么样的工作 \N{\rEng}What kind of job did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.41,0:27:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那种工作\N{\rEng}That kind of job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.66,0:27:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为企业执行安保\N{\rEng}It's babysitting corporates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.21,0:27:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么危险的\N{\rEng}It's not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.42,0:27:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再和我说了\N{\rEng}Don’t tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.17,0:27:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在说谎\N{\rEng}Now I know you’re lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没有 看着我 我没有\N{\rEng}No, I’m not. Look at me. I’m not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.34,0:27:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 我得照顾好我的家人\N{\rEng}Baby, I need to take care of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.60,0:27:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会错过杰克生日的\N{\rEng}You’re gonna miss Jack's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机在8小时后起飞\N{\rEng}Flight departs in eight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大广场 停止战争
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.21,0:29:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你花了超过15分钟才到这里 \N{\rEng}It take you longer than 15 minutes to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.42,0:29:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只花了8分钟\N{\rEng}Only took me eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨利姆·穆欣 42岁 病毒学荣誉教授\N{\rEng}Salim Mohsin, 42. Professor Emeritus of virology.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.30,0:29:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柏林洪堡大学\N{\rEng}Humboldt-Universität, Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他每月都会上那里讲几次课\N{\rEng}He lectures there a few times a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.02,0:29:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他主要是从事研究工作\N{\rEng}but his primary focus is research work
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究工作是在城东40公里处一个私人实验室进行的\N{\rEng}which is conducted at a private laboratory 40 kilometers east of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.52,0:29:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁等级 \N{\rEng}Threat level?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.73,0:29:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生化恐怖主义 A级\N{\rEng}It's bioterrorism. Category A.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.07,0:29:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车就在停车场 菲亚特Tipo\N{\rEng}Car is in the parking lot. Fiat Tipo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.30,0:33:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨利姆 \N{\rEng}Salim?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.15,0:33:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终止监视 清理好现场 下午4点於#732会合
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.71,0:34:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起床了 早餐都弄好了\N{\rEng}Wakey-wakey, eggs and bakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.30,0:34:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到锺起床了\N{\rEng}Time to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.19,0:34:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都把任务简报记熟\N{\rEng}Baseball cards stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨利姆·穆罕默德·穆欣 42岁\N{\rEng}Salim Mohamed Mohsin. Age 42.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.24,0:34:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叙利亚裔 身高6尺1 体重190磅\N{\rEng}Syrian descent. 6’1", 190 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.24,0:34:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡子有染过 左耳位置后方有个心形胎记\N{\rEng}Dyes his beard. Heart-shaped birthmark behind his left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.58,0:34:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的右手腕上也有圆形的胎记\N{\rEng}Round-shaped birthmark on his right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.71,0:34:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈佛医学院毕业 并获得联邦研究基金资助\N{\rEng}Harvard Med. Graduates and receives a federal research grant
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以研究人类史中的致病性流感病毒\N{\rEng}to study pathogenic influenza viruses in humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.55,0:35:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H1N1以及其他亚种\N{\rEng}H1N1 and avian flu mutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.55,0:35:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但资助未能被延长\N{\rEng}His grant was not extended.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.26,0:35:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此他和他家人搬到了柏林 在这里继续他的研究\N{\rEng}His family relocated here to Berlin where he continued his research.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资助人是法鲁克·奥杰\N{\rEng}Financed by Farouk Ojjeh,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.06,0:35:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥达瓦的创始人 这是个与基地 叙利亚有联系的慈善机构\N{\rEng}the founder of Al Dawaa, a charity with known links to al-Qaeda and Syria.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.94,0:35:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是布局图\N{\rEng}This is a layout
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.03,0:35:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们内部线人提供\N{\rEng}annotated by our inside asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.74,0:35:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该实验室只有很少的安保\N{\rEng}The lab only has moderate security presence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.20,0:35:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为警报装置是与柏林警方直连的\N{\rEng}since the guard shack is connected to Berlin police.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.95,0:35:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验室都什么样的门  不知道\N{\rEng}-What kind of doors are they? -No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们怎么进入  生物识别 保安的手指\N{\rEng}How are we breaching? - Biometrics. Guard's thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.33,0:35:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当目标人物被抓捕完后呢 \N{\rEng}What happens when we hit jackpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.92,0:35:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对他进行战术审讯\N{\rEng}We conduct a tactical interrogation,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.05,0:35:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后联系上级 等待进一步的指示\N{\rEng}then contact higher and wait for further instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.89,0:35:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家从这片树林撤离后\N{\rEng}Exfil back through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.93,0:35:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后到这里会合\N{\rEng}Link up with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.18,0:35:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着大家直接去机场\N{\rEng}And then it's straight to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.89,0:35:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机会在1号停机坪准备好\N{\rEng}Plane will be ready at Airfield Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都知道激进分子会干出些什么\N{\rEng}We all know what one motivated radical can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.77,0:35:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我们加油 完成任务 然后回到家人身边\N{\rEng}so let's cowboy-up, get it done and go home to our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.36,0:36:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\rEng}Giddyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.62,0:36:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始检查 野狼\N{\rEng}- Go live. - Wolf Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.66,0:36:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸\N{\rEng}Fox Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.16,0:36:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲛鱼\N{\rEng}Sierra One.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.67,0:36:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郊狼\N{\rEng}Coyote One.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.72,0:37:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好准备\N{\rEng}Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.81,0:38:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩7分钟\N{\rEng}Seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.93,0:39:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来\N{\rEng}Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.01,0:39:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做什么 \N{\rEng}Was ist das?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.56,0:39:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站好\N{\rEng}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.11,0:39:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩6分钟\N{\rEng}Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.57,0:39:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要问你些问题\N{\rEng}Need to ask you questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.49,0:39:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁有实验室权限 \N{\rEng}Who has access to the lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.53,0:39:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我 只有我有权限...\N{\rEng}Oh. Only me. I have access. It’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.79,0:39:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛姬·博列夫斯基\N{\rEng}Maggie Bolevska.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.29,0:39:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她是我的...\N{\rEng}Y-Yeah. She's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.71,0:39:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的研究助理 她也有权限\N{\rEng}She's my research assistant. She has access.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.05,0:39:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁知道你工作的具体内容 \N{\rEng}Who else knows the specifics of your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.76,0:39:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人了 你们是什么人 \N{\rEng}Nobody. Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.38,0:39:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的资助人呢 \N{\rEng}Your financier?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.43,0:39:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他知道我的工作内容 但他...\N{\rEng}Y-Yeah, he knows about my work, but he...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:39:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是科学家 他不过... 是个投资人 他....\N{\rEng}He's not a scientist. He's a... He's an investor. He’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.64,0:40:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把你的工作备份都放在哪 \N{\rEng}Where do you back up your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.85,0:40:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在离你家附近的地方 还有一对人马在待命中\N{\rEng}There's another team on standby a block away from your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.32,0:40:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好合作 不然他们出什么事可不要怪我\N{\rEng}Cooperate. There is no limit to what we are authorized to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.86,0:40:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把你的工作备份都放在哪 \N{\rEng}Where do you back up your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都在这 就在这些电脑里\N{\rEng}It's all in here. It's in these computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.66,0:40:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他备份了\N{\rEng}There are no lines in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.58,0:40:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到了\N{\rEng}We got it. Payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.25,0:40:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想要的是钱 我可以给你钱 这不是问题\N{\rEng}If it's money you want, I can arrange money. It's really not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.92,0:40:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他头转过去\N{\rEng}Head against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.21,0:40:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说... 我真的可以...\N{\rEng}I mean... I can really...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.10,0:40:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳机\N{\rEng}Ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.52,0:40:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲛鱼刚触发了警报\N{\rEng}Sierra just got a hit off the scanner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方正从柏林赶来\N{\rEng}Police are inbound from Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.74,0:40:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待牧场方面下达指示\N{\rEng}Awaiting instructions from the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.24,0:41:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代号指令X\N{\rEng}Code X.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.37,0:41:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不留活口 \N{\rEng}All the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.37,0:41:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不留活口\N{\rEng}All the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.75,0:41:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做成工业事故 我们还有五分钟\N{\rEng}Industrial accident. We got five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.50,0:41:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把笔记本带上 去掉他们手铐和头套 我们从没到过这里\N{\rEng}Bag the laptop. Lose the cuffs and hoods. We were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.19,0:41:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定萨利姆\N{\rEng}Get Salim.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥... 大哥 大哥 求你了 这整件事\N{\rEng}Sir... Sir. Sir, please. This whole thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是个误会 我只不过... 是个搞科研的而已\N{\rEng}It's a misunderstanding. I’m a... I’m a man of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.71,0:41:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是... 这就是个天大的误会\N{\rEng}This is... This is a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.13,0:41:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 我真是搞科研的...\N{\rEng}Sir! I’m a man of sci...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.22,0:42:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是搞科研的 我还有家庭 求你了\N{\rEng}I’m a man of science. I have a family, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 求你了 我还有家庭 求你了\N{\rEng}Sir, please. I have a family. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 停下 停下 停下 停下\N{\rEng}No! No! No, no, stop, stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.81,0:42:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁派你来的 \N{\rEng}Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.06,0:42:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至知道你在为谁工作吗 \N{\rEng}Do you even know who you’re working for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.40,0:42:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道你在做什么\N{\rEng}You don’t know what you’re doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.03,0:42:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 求你了 听着\N{\rEng}Stop! Please, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.11,0:42:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的研究将会拯救数百万人的生命\N{\rEng}The research I’m doing will save millions of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.49,0:42:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\rEng}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.45,0:42:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 停下 求你了\N{\rEng}Stop. Stop, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.04,0:42:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想要祈祷 现在可以开始了\N{\rEng}If you wanna say a prayer, now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷  我不相信什么神 我只相信科学\N{\rEng}A prayer? I don’t believe in God. I believe in science.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.13,0:42:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\rEng}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.42,0:42:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的保险箱还有一份我所有数据的备份\N{\rEng}I keep a copy of all my data in a safety deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.51,0:42:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还有良知 就把它取出来\N{\rEng}If you have a conscience, get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.01,0:42:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界将会需要它的\N{\rEng}The world will need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.09,0:42:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 停下 求你 停下\N{\rEng}Stop, stop. Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.43,0:42:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要伤害我的家人\N{\rEng}Please don’t hurt my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.97,0:42:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要伤害我的家人 停下 求你了\N{\rEng}Don’t hurt my family. Stop. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要\N{\rEng}Don’t! Don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲛鱼 2分钟后接我们\N{\rEng}Sierra One, RV in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.17,0:43:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.64,0:43:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要超时了 赶紧走\N{\rEng}We’re in OT. Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.77,0:43:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是马鲛鱼 一分钟后到\N{\rEng}Sierra One. One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.97,0:44:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草 是警察 9点钟方向\N{\rEng}Fuck. - Cops,00.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 警察\N{\rEng}Halt! Polizei!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.31,0:44:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动\N{\rEng}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.73,0:44:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动中\N{\rEng}Moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.19,0:44:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向你左侧\N{\rEng}On your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.37,0:44:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸中弹\N{\rEng}Fox Two is hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.30,0:44:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制住\N{\rEng}Suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.14,0:44:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包 把包丢我 收到\N{\rEng}The bag. Throw it to me. - Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.60,0:44:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把包丢我\N{\rEng}Throw it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.19,0:44:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸倒下了\N{\rEng}Fox Two down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.85,0:44:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护我\N{\rEng}Cover fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.19,0:45:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.37,0:45:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况 \N{\rEng}Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.08,0:45:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左腿中弹\N{\rEng}Left leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.95,0:45:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有人来了\N{\rEng}New contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.63,0:45:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲛鱼中弹\N{\rEng}Sierra's hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.72,0:45:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放倒她\N{\rEng}Put her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.23,0:45:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们离开这里\N{\rEng}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.20,0:45:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来 我们走\N{\rEng}Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.50,0:46:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.85,0:46:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的膝盖废了\N{\rEng}My knee is fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.31,0:46:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先把你放下来 妈的\N{\rEng}I’m gonna have to set you down. Ah, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.40,0:46:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把装备丢了 能轻松些\N{\rEng}Dump the gear, save the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.62,0:46:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扶着你 快走 快走\N{\rEng}I got you. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.30,0:48:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打死了警察\N{\rEng}We shot cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.76,0:48:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是迫不得已\N{\rEng}Did what we had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.06,0:48:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笔记本没事吧 \N{\rEng}Is the laptop secure?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.98,0:48:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\rEng}It's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.44,0:48:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到了笔记本 任务首位\N{\rEng}We got the laptop. Mission first.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.07,0:48:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须给你输血 是A型血吗 \N{\rEng}I have to give you blood. Confirm A-pos?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.53,0:48:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}A-pos.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.53,0:48:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们中得有人去送笔记本\N{\rEng}One of us has to walk this in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.41,0:48:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不输血 你就会死的\N{\rEng}If you don’t get blood, you’re gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.66,0:48:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去送吧\N{\rEng}You bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.75,0:48:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的 我不会丢下你\N{\rEng}Fuck you. I’m not leaving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.96,0:48:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人\N{\rEng}My family.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.00,0:48:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能把我的事告诉克莉丝汀\N{\rEng}I want Christine to hear about me from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.30,0:48:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去告诉他们 迈克 你自己去和他们说\N{\rEng}You tell ’em yourself, Mike. You’re gonna tell ’em yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.55,0:48:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你答应我\N{\rEng}I want it to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带我们回家的 你听到没 \N{\rEng}I’m gonna get us home. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.06,0:49:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们将对柏林爆炸枪战案进行更深入的了解\N{\rEng}With us now to shed more light on the explosion and gunfight in Berlin
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.23,0:49:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请安全专家威廉·索诺比\N{\rEng}is security expert William Sonobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉 你能... 你能给我们一些关於案发现场的新信息吗 \N{\rEng}Uh, William, can you... can you give us any new information on this critical scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.57,0:49:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你邀请我 艾丽卡\N{\rEng}Thanks for having me on, Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.11,0:49:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国政府正在积极向我们的\N{\rEng}US officials have been active in offering aid
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.36,0:49:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德国朋友提供援助和情报支持\N{\rEng}and intelligence support to our German friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.04,0:50:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再救我的命了\N{\rEng}You have to stop saving my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.04,0:50:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在欠我两回了\N{\rEng}That makes two you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.96,0:50:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈是怎么把我背出来的 \N{\rEng}How the fuck did you carry me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.55,0:50:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么计划是什么 \N{\rEng}So what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.10,0:50:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把笔记本带回去 拿到报酬 再去喝杯啤酒\N{\rEng}We get the laptop home. Let's get paid. Let's have a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.22,0:50:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.95,0:50:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了 你自己走吧\N{\rEng}I’m down. You take it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.45,0:50:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 说好的一起走\N{\rEng}No, no. We go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.87,0:50:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在得改变下计划\N{\rEng}I’ll compromise the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.04,0:50:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道那个包里有什么\N{\rEng}We don’t know what's in that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.75,0:50:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它带回去 你先走 我马上就来\N{\rEng}Get it home. You go. I’ll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.63,0:50:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去取得联系 然后再回来\N{\rEng}I’ll make contact. I’ll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.42,0:51:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 回到这个四季酒店管道分店 \N{\rEng}Yeah. Back to the Four Seasons of Tunnels?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.93,0:51:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我没事的\N{\rEng}Come on. I’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.26,0:51:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会藏身暗处 我只是需要24小时来恢复下\N{\rEng}I’ll move in the dark. I just need 24 hours to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.81,0:51:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快他妈走吧\N{\rEng}Get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.86,0:51:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.71,0:51:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去到柏林\N{\rEng}- I head to Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.63,0:51:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个交出去\N{\rEng}- Hand this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.92,0:51:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得联系 安排好车 48小时后回家\N{\rEng}Make contact. RV in 48. Forty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.84,0:51:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在瑟维纳酒店 安排好我们的东西\N{\rEng}Hotel Salvina. I’m gonna get everything we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.51,0:51:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,48小时\N{\rEng}Forty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.68,0:51:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能被活捉\N{\rEng}Capture's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.34,0:51:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被活捉\N{\rEng}Not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.93,0:52:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我游出去 直到我开始怀疑我还能否再游回来\N{\rEng}I swim out until I start to wonder if I can make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.73,0:54:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯\N{\rEng}James!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.78,0:54:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.61,0:54:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回来 孩子\N{\rEng}Get back here, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.97,0:55:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 欢迎光临\N{\rEng}Hallo. Willkommen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.43,0:55:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取房\N{\rEng}Uh, Ketner.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.56,0:55:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出示护照\N{\rEng}Reisepass, bitte.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.69,0:55:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEng}Danke schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.94,0:55:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.03,0:55:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEng}Mmm. Danke schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.59,0:56:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已做好安排 这里很安全 上午10点见 药在床头柜里 6小时一次\N{\rEng}Hallo?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.46,0:57:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.96,0:57:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪里 \N{\rEng}Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.76,0:57:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 嗨\N{\rEng}Hallo. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.98,0:58:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是拉斯蒂 说吧\N{\rEng}This is Rusty. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.27,0:58:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的一次性电话 并不安全\N{\rEng}I’m on a burner. It's not secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.56,0:58:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.65,0:58:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别无选择了 身体状况如何 \N{\rEng}We don’t have a choice. Physical condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.90,0:58:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤 但并不严重\N{\rEng}Compromised but not critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.53,0:58:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼有与你联系吗 \N{\rEng}Did Wolf Two make contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.20,0:58:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼没能活着抵达柏林\N{\rEng}Wolf Two never made it to Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.45,0:58:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派了一支救援队前往酒店 然后带你去机场\N{\rEng}I’ve got an extraction team en route to the hotel, get you over to the airfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.70,0:58:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在哪 \N{\rEng}Confirm location.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.84,0:58:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在吗  你现在在哪 \N{\rEng}Hey, stay with me. Confirm location.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.34,0:58:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我野狼的遭遇 我再告诉你位置\N{\rEng}I’ll do that when you brief me on Wolf Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.55,0:58:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你安全后 我会给你份完整报告\N{\rEng}You’ll get a full brief when you’re secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.59,0:58:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在情况已经变得不可收拾 我们已严重被暴露\N{\rEng}Right now everything is extremely fubar, and we are highly exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.06,0:58:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我现在所做的一切就是为了让你能回家\N{\rEng}Listen to me. Everything I am doing right now is to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.93,0:58:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你能安然无恙的回到牧场 你懂吗 \N{\rEng}Back to the ranch safe and sound. You feel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.98,0:58:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官 当然 那就告诉我你在哪里\N{\rEng}-Yes, sir. Of course. -Then confirm your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.23,0:58:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大广场 到处是警察\N{\rEng}Alexanderplatz. Heavy police.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.07,0:58:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大广场 收到 这就来\N{\rEng}Alexanderplatz. Copy that. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.03,0:59:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让他们改道去艾尔森桥要多久\N{\rEng}How long to reroute them to the Elsen Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.20,0:59:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15到20分钟\N{\rEng}Fifteen, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.91,0:59:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你沿着水走\N{\rEng}I need you to start heading for the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.74,0:59:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直朝着埃尔森桥方向走 西北角 预计15到20分钟\N{\rEng}Down towards the Elsen Bridge. Northwest corner. Fifteen, 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.28,0:59:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是拉斯蒂 说吧\N{\rEng}This is Rusty. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.32,0:59:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经到达埃尔森桥 西北角\N{\rEng}I’m at the Elsen Bridge. Northwest corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.45,0:59:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棕色宝马X1 看到没\N{\rEng}Brown BMW X1. Confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.33,0:59:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到\N{\rEng}Confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.62,0:59:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.89,1:00:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果野狼没有到达柏林 那他是如何安排我撤离的\N{\rEng}If Wolf Two didn’t make it to Berlin, how’d he arrange my exfil then?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.56,1:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我知道 现在情形看起来很可疑\N{\rEng}Look, I understand. Right now nothing makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.86,1:00:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要相信我 我现在正在帮你\N{\rEng}But you gotta trust me. I am trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这样帮的迈克 \N{\rEng}Same way you helped Mike?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.49,1:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 你是不是杀了他 \N{\rEng}You motherfucker. Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.20,1:00:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在为谁工作 \N{\rEng}Who are we working for?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.37,1:00:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再像个孩子一样 赶快他妈的上车\N{\rEng}Stop acting like a child and get in the fucking car.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.62,1:00:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样 我一定会杀了你\N{\rEng}If this goes down, I’m gonna come for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.83,1:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快他妈的上车\N{\rEng}Get in the fucking car.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.92,1:00:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.16,1:03:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是美国人 \N{\rEng}You American?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.62,1:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈海军陆战队的 \N{\rEng}You’re a fucking marine?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.62,1:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你海军陆战队的 \N{\rEng}Are you a marine?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.17,1:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是 隶属侦察连\N{\rEng}Was. Recon.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.88,1:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是什么 \N{\rEng}What was your mission?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.01,1:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,营救\N{\rEng}Extraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.76,1:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着牧场发出了指令\N{\rEng}Then the ranch gave an audible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.43,1:04:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到人后就处死\N{\rEng}Terminate after pickup.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.14,1:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候 \N{\rEng}When?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.19,1:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在桥上 我看到你的时候\N{\rEng}On the bridge, when I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.61,1:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搭档 是不是也是你干的 \N{\rEng}My partner, you go after him? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.36,1:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说他们把他带走了 抱歉\N{\rEng}I heard they picked him up. I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.03,1:04:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说 我们是在拯救生命 但却是自相残杀\N{\rEng}They told us we’d be saving lives, not killing our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.20,1:04:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的... 照片 请还我\N{\rEng}My... ...picture, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.14,1:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里... 有一间安全屋\N{\rEng}There is... There's a safe house.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.90,1:05:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个密码联络\N{\rEng}Use this code for pickup.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.44,1:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着我的手机\N{\rEng}Take my phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.07,1:05:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝不能回家去\N{\rEng}You can never go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.33,1:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把确认指令Tomahawk\N{\rEng}The kill code is Tomahawk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.79,1:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发送过去 能为你拖延一阵\N{\rEng}It’ll stop the team, at least for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.09,1:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯蒂说他会带我们发家致富\N{\rEng}Rusty said he’d make us all rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.60,1:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身上有没备份
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.03,1:08:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快递\N{\rEng}Kurier.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.16,1:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 \N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.41,1:08:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁  你想要做什么 \N{\rEng}- Shh. - Who are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.62,1:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁 \N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.70,1:08:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这并不想伤害你或你家人\N{\rEng}I’m not here to hurt you or your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.62,1:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你不回答我的所有问题 我会的\N{\rEng}But if you don’t answer all of my questions, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.17,1:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫把工作研究放在个保险箱里 我要知道它在哪\N{\rEng}Your husband secured his work someplace safe. I need to know where.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.26,1:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔薇 看着我 看着我\N{\rEng}Sylvie, look at me. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.26,1:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想雅尼斯和奥利维亚 快告诉我\N{\rEng}For Yanis, for Olivier. Tell me where.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.72,1:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞士信贷银行 瑞士信贷银行 \N{\rEng}- Swiss Credit Bank. - Swiss Credit Bank?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.31,1:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在保险箱里 保险箱里\N{\rEng}- Safe deposit box. - Safe deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.86,1:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别伤害我儿子\N{\rEng}Don’t hurt my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.11,1:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸 不会有事的\N{\rEng}Shh, just breathe. It's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.99,1:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去穿戴好 好的\N{\rEng}- Tell him to get ready. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.53,1:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他 我是他爸爸的老朋友 我们要一起去吃午饭\N{\rEng}You tell him I’m an old friend of his dad’s, and we’re going out for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.42,1:08:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅尼斯\N{\rEng}Yanis.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.17,1:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.29,1:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我一起去\N{\rEng}He's coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.62,1:09:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会在这里等你回来\N{\rEng}We’ll be here when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.32,1:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他的朋友 \N{\rEng}You were his friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.41,1:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.75,1:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难过吗 \N{\rEng}Are you sad?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.54,1:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.76,1:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rEng}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.17,1:11:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪认识的 \N{\rEng}Where did you meet?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.13,1:11:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴黎\N{\rEng}Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.67,1:11:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头胎是在哪出生的 \N{\rEng}Where was your first child born?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.09,1:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生在... 闭上嘴\N{\rEng}I was born... Tais-toi!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.22,1:11:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有两个孩子要养\N{\rEng}I have two boys to raise.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.14,1:11:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有一切都被你夺走了\N{\rEng}Everything we have is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.23,1:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\N{\rEng}Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.36,1:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅尼斯出生在波士顿\N{\rEng}Um... Yanis was born in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.33,1:11:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算为你第三胎取什么名字 \N{\rEng}What were you gonna call your third child?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.25,1:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔丹\N{\rEng}Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.88,1:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把车停下\N{\rEng}Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.68,1:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 他们付了你多少钱 嗯 \N{\rEng}So, how much did they pay you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.43,1:12:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望这值得你卖命\N{\rEng}I hope it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.88,1:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位 \N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.13,1:12:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察连 6-22-34 求救\N{\rEng}Recon. 6-22-34. Mayday.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.80,1:12:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 位置 \N{\rEng}Copy. Location?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.17,1:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏林\N{\rEng}Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.05,1:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎样 \N{\rEng}Condition?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.14,1:12:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以移动\N{\rEng}Mobile.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.22,1:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天凌晨3点 GPS坐标 14.98 51.150\N{\rEng}0300 tomorrow. GPS 14.98, 51.150.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.20,1:13:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷路了 \N{\rEng}Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.87,1:13:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你介意把枪放下吗 \N{\rEng}Do you mind lowering the gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.46,1:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你打给我的\N{\rEng}You called me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.68,1:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上车就放下枪\N{\rEng}It's the price of admission.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.22,1:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在崩溃之前
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.35,1:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还能承受多少
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.57,1:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能别再挣扎了\N{\rEng}There's no need to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.24,1:14:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的包在哪 \N{\rEng}Where's my bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.26,1:14:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么... 我们没事了 \N{\rEng}So... are we good?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.87,1:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 你在这很安全\N{\rEng}It's okay. You’re safe here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.24,1:15:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我处理了你的膝盖 它感染得很严重\N{\rEng}I cleaned your knee. It was badly infected.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.62,1:15:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,265)}你的{\u1}ACL{\u0}撕裂了 我不知道你怎么弄得 但你弄撕裂了 {\c&HC38E15&\fs14}（*ACL：前交叉韧带）\N{\rEng}You tore your ACL. I don’t know how you walked on it, but you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.21,1:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个陆战队员告诉了我你的事...\N{\rEng}The marine who told me about you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.76,1:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识他 \N{\rEng}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.42,1:15:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.22,1:15:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了他吗 \N{\rEng}Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.76,1:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但我知道他们训练我们为他们跑腿\N{\rEng}No, but I know they train us to run their errands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.14,1:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死他们的敌人 甚至自相残杀\N{\rEng}Kill their enemies and kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.77,1:15:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓"国家安全" 只不过是遮掩这一切肮脏勾当的借口\N{\rEng}"National security." It's just a rock they can hide their dirty shit under.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.86,1:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要回去\N{\rEng}I need to get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.36,1:15:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回哪去 \N{\rEng}Back where?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.44,1:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去\N{\rEng}Back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.41,1:15:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想了\N{\rEng}That's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.66,1:15:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也回不去了\N{\rEng}Home is a memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.46,1:15:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要... 你差点死了\N{\rEng}You need... You almost died.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.17,1:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体需要休息 我没事\N{\rEng}- Your body needs rest. - I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.01,1:16:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 我没事\N{\rEng}- Shh. All right. - I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.52,1:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅尼斯 万一我无法亲口告诉你这些\N{\rEng}Yanis, in case I’m not here to tell you this in person,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.94,1:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.40,1:16:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道在过去几年里 我一直缺席於你的人生\N{\rEng}I know you have felt my absence these last few years.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.57,1:16:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你知道原因\N{\rEng}I need you to know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.49,1:16:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早就下定了决心\N{\rEng}I made up my mind very early
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.70,1:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子们绝不能生活在恐惧下\N{\rEng}that my children would live without fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.25,1:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此 我选择了将我的一生献给科学界\N{\rEng}And because of that, I chose to dedicate my life to science.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.08,1:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是 有些有权势的人不仅无视科学\N{\rEng}Unfortunately, there are powerful people who ignore science,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.38,1:16:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还为了自己的私利想利用它\N{\rEng}even subvert it for their own personal gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.47,1:16:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅尼斯 在你手中的是我毕生研究\N{\rEng}Yanis, in your hands is my life's work:
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.55,1:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以预防致死率为16%的H5N1疫苗资料\N{\rEng}the vaccine for the H5N1 virus with a mortality rate of 16%.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.35,1:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为它才坐在这里 对着这个摄像头却不是你的双眼\N{\rEng}It may have landed me in this chair, staring into this camera instead of your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.77,1:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想让你知道 你的父亲在为一些东西奋斗\N{\rEng}but I want you to know that your father stood for something,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.24,1:17:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所奋斗的东西 只要能有你的帮助\N{\rEng}created something that with your help
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.07,1:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便我被他们杀死后 仍将能造福於人类\N{\rEng}will benefit humanity long after they’ve shot me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.33,1:17:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的是 如果恰巧爆发了疾病\N{\rEng}It is very important that this vaccine is available
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.25,1:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大众便能够免费使用到这些疫苗\N{\rEng}free to the public should the unthinkable happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.68,1:17:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的主 感谢你赐予我这顿美餐\N{\rEng}Dear Lord, thank you for this meal
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.31,1:17:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将我的客人安全带到这里\N{\rEng}and bringing my guest here safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.14,1:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请宽恕我们的罪 让我们免於地狱业火\N{\rEng}Forgive us our sins and keep us from the fires of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.06,1:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿我们灵魂能升入天堂\N{\rEng}May our souls go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.65,1:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那些需要被怜悯的 阿门\N{\rEng}Especially those in need of thy mercy. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.23,1:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\rEng}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.61,1:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的纹身 OD3224\N{\rEng}Your tat. OD3224.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.70,1:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,265)}代表你服役於{\u1}"矛头部队"{\u0} {\fs14\c&HC38E15&}（*矛头部队：用以泛指现在在战区前线参与打击任务的部队）\N{\rEng}That's tip of the spear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.50,1:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 他们让我们很忙\N{\rEng}Yeah, they kept us busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.50,1:17:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伊拉克还是阿富汗 \N{\rEng}In Iraq or Afghanistan?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.42,1:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边\N{\rEng}Both.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.80,1:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过兴都库什吗 \N{\rEng}You ever been to Hindu Kush?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.52,1:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山峰如此之高 你会认为彷佛天堂就在这之上\N{\rEng}Mountains so high, you think heaven's resting on ’em.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.23,1:18:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山谷如此之绿 你会认为彷佛这就是伊甸\N{\rEng}The valleys so green, you think it's Eden.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.02,1:18:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才去时 还以为是来了科罗拉多州\N{\rEng}I thought I was in Colorado when I first saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.66,1:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道 我们曾连续12天为\N{\rEng}You know, we were on a 12-day straight
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.08,1:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找我们当地人的一个孩子\N{\rEng}looking for one of our local guys’ kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.79,1:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打猎的时候 走失了... 没能找到他 可怜的家伙\N{\rEng}Been gone... Gone hunting, couldn’t find him. Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.88,1:18:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我们找到了个偏僻的院落 接着我们打开院门\N{\rEng}So we broke down a door on this out-of-the-way compound,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.22,1:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后冲了进去\N{\rEng}and then we burst in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.30,1:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在清查完房间后 我们找到了那个孩子\N{\rEng}And once we cleared everything, we found him, the kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.60,1:18:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子 他被铁链锁在墙上 哭得很伤心\N{\rEng}And he was chained to the wall, just crying his eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.89,1:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在隔壁房 里面全是女孩\N{\rEng}But in the next room, it's full of girls
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.73,1:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四散躺着 全死了\N{\rEng}all strung out, splayed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.48,1:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后站在她们之中的是一只狗\N{\rEng}And in the middle of all this was a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.07,1:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只小家伙\N{\rEng}It's just a little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.70,1:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼吉 它很高兴\N{\rEng}Mangy. Happy as can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.32,1:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它看到我们很高兴 它浑身脏乱 叫唤着\N{\rEng}Happy to see us. All yelps and matted hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.79,1:19:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这事件里 我唯一能记得的也就是那条狗了\N{\rEng}And all that shit, and the thing I remember the most is the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.42,1:19:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那条狗在经历这一切后仍然能做回它自己\N{\rEng}’Cause that dog survived all that shit without even blinking an eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.60,1:19:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一死了之很容易\N{\rEng}It's much easier to kill,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.81,1:19:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要活着却很艰难\N{\rEng}but it's harder to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.11,1:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里待多久了 \N{\rEng}How long you been out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.53,1:19:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13年了\N{\rEng}Thirteen years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.46,1:20:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有家庭吗 \N{\rEng}You have a family?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.17,1:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我有个妻子 两个漂亮的女儿\N{\rEng}Yeah, I’ve got a wife, two beautiful girls,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.17,1:20:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的房子\N{\rEng}a nice house.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.09,1:20:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不和她们联系吗 \N{\rEng}You ever feel like reaching out?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.22,1:20:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我和她们一起...\N{\rEng}When I reach out...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.43,1:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总做错事\N{\rEng}I break things.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.65,1:20:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都有心魔这东西\N{\rEng}We all know the monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.52,1:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而它有时候会控制着你\N{\rEng}And sometimes he comes to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.99,1:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛排怎么样 \N{\rEng}How's the steak?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.04,1:20:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃过更好的\N{\rEng}I’ve had better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.92,1:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 我也是\N{\rEng}So... So have I.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.23,1:23:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人  是的\N{\rEng}- American? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.52,1:23:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路安全 先生\N{\rEng}Safe travels, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.22,1:24:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能把我的事告诉克莉丝汀\N{\rEng}I want Christine to hear about me from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.02,1:24:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去告诉他们 迈克 你自己去和他们说\N{\rEng}You tell ’em yourself, Mike. Tell ’em yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.93,1:25:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个混蛋\N{\rEng}Motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.18,1:27:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来我家干什么 \N{\rEng}Doing at my house?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.76,1:27:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我\N{\rEng}Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.23,1:27:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对我开枪吗 \N{\rEng}You wanna shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.69,1:27:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\rEng}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.33,1:27:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上你家去告诉克莉丝汀 就像你让我做的那样\N{\rEng}I went to your house to tell Christine, like you asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.66,1:27:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯蒂说过... 你知道他想要除掉我的事吗 \N{\rEng}-Rusty said... -Did you know he was coming after me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.08,1:27:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说你没能幸存下来\N{\rEng}He said you didn’t make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.79,1:27:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要骗我 \N{\rEng}Why did you lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.09,1:27:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你什么  去你的\N{\rEng}About what? - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.05,1:27:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的归属 抱团取暖 光荣的工作\N{\rEng}A real home. A tribe. Honorable work.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.01,1:27:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本是为了抢劫数据 所有一切都不该发生的\N{\rEng}It was a data heist. None of this was supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.43,1:27:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它发生了 所以为了什么 \N{\rEng}But it did happen. And for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.51,1:27:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了一票捞够\N{\rEng}Payday of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.89,1:28:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们偷的并不是数据\N{\rEng}What we stole was not data.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.02,1:28:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这些混蛋想要释放的病毒的解药\N{\rEng}It's a cure to a virus these fuckers wanna release.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.77,1:28:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便他们能在人们的痛苦中狂捞几十亿 你知道这个吗 \N{\rEng}So they can make billions off people suffering. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.78,1:28:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈这样做良心过意的去 \N{\rEng}How do you fucking live with yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.78,1:28:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要养家 尤其是我的儿子\N{\rEng}I got a family and a son with special needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.70,1:28:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我家人 我儿子 他们就不是了 \N{\rEng}So what about my family? My son! Their needs!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.41,1:28:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有一切都安排妥当\N{\rEng}Everything's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.91,1:28:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会有一大笔钱付给布莱安和你儿子 四百万\N{\rEng}There's a huge payout to Brianne and your boy. Four million.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.33,1:28:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们以后都将会衣食无忧\N{\rEng}They’ll never want for anything ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.04,1:28:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢  我呢 \N{\rEng}Except for me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.46,1:28:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能回家去\N{\rEng}You can’t go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.01,1:28:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他如果发现你在这里 他会用尽所有手段来对付你\N{\rEng}He finds out you’re here, he's gonna come after you with everything he's got.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.51,1:28:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做了那么多\N{\rEng}After everything we’ve done,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.10,1:28:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了那么多\N{\rEng}everything we’ve been through.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.47,1:28:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我他妈的为你流血\N{\rEng}I fucking bled for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.35,1:28:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我换来什么 \N{\rEng}And this is what I get?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.49,1:29:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 别这样做\N{\rEng}James, don’t do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.96,1:29:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.45,1:29:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲...\N{\rEng}My father, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.70,1:29:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给我打上了同样的印记\N{\rEng}He branded me to be like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.50,1:29:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  我们他妈... 骨子里一模一样\N{\rEng}You know, a fucking... a fucking Ranger to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.00,1:29:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当军队不再需要他 把他赶走的时候\N{\rEng}And when they cut him loose and they cast him out,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.92,1:29:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他再也没回过家里\N{\rEng}he just never came home.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.22,1:30:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此消失 没有留言 屍体 他妈什么也没有\N{\rEng}Vanished. No note, corpse. Fucking nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.27,1:30:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后只能... 把那混蛋给我的全部东西都埋在后院洞里\N{\rEng}I finally just buried all the... shit the fucker ever gave me in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.19,1:30:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自给他举行了葬礼\N{\rEng}Had my own funeral.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.87,1:30:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就站在那洞口前 可悲的看着他那些垃圾东西\N{\rEng}I’m standing over this pathetic little hole filled with stupid shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.99,1:30:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后对自己发誓 我永远都不要成他那样\N{\rEng}And I swore to myself I would never be like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.29,1:30:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都不会抛弃我的家人 你能懂这些吗 \N{\rEng}I would never forsake my family. Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.50,1:30:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果拉斯蒂发现你在这\N{\rEng}Rusty finds out you’re here,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.55,1:30:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就会去对付你的家人\N{\rEng}he's gonna come after your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.72,1:30:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要结束这事只有一个办法\N{\rEng}There's only one way this ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.19,1:31:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  迈克\N{\rEng}Hey, what's up, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.56,1:31:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有啤酒吗  他在哪里 \N{\rEng}You got a beer? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.81,1:31:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在厨房里\N{\rEng}He's in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.32,1:34:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想着能战死在沙场上\N{\rEng}Always wanted to die with my boots on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.72,1:34:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了正确的事\N{\rEng}I got a room prepped and ready for ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.02,1:34:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回家了 迈克\N{\rEng}We’re going home, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.56,1:35:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放点该死的音乐\N{\rEng}Put some fucking music on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.77,1:35:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.49,1:35:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷\N{\rEng}Cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.84,1:35:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我...\N{\rEng}Tell my s...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.68,1:35:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子...\N{\rEng}My son...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有碌碌而死\N{\rEng}I didn’t die in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.07,1:35:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rEng}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.99,1:35:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.37,1:36:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊 深水炸弹\N{\rEng}Yeah! Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.17,1:36:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.18,1:36:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游得不错\N{\rEng}Good job!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.67,1:37:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack!

